{"tid":247150,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"老細捱飯盒我吃日本嘢，釋懷了。","createTime":"2017-05-17T14:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T04:27:20.000Z","uid":34252,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c892bf519247baebc809fa71d1c9247cb521b8e","tid":247150,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"話說尋日下午有客嚟，老細午飯都不敢行開，只能叫人買個叉雞飯哩埋喺房食，吖仲加杯凍鴛鴦。<br />\n我為免佢失驚無神嗌我呢樣嗰樣，梗係幾大都唔留喺office喇，自己出去食咗碗豬骨湯味長崎拉麵；吃飽返嚟見到老細滿咀油，搵張爛鬼厠紙喺度卒吓卒吓...<br />\n當刻，我個心真係釋懷了，曾經好羨慕老細風光的日子，我好喜歡現在的工作和生活模式，原來我已經升呢，老細都係捱飯盒，而我就吃日本嘢，覺得好多嘢都放都低晒了，人也輕鬆了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtRSW_zogiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOtRSW_zogiw&d=oZ19EkYl1LXsHPE32KnJvW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a38b5e04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OtRSW_zogiw</a>"},{"pid":"27208c37aeb4f35ea8636a78b4536f4f6156d329","tid":247150,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}